org.hibernate.metamodel.model.domain.spi

Interface VirtualNavigable<J>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    DomainType<J>, DomainTypeDescriptor<J>, ExpressableType<J>, Navigable<J>, Serializable, Type<J>, Writeable
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    DiscriminatorDescriptor<J>, EntityIdentifierCompositeNonAggregated<O,J>, RowIdDescriptor<J>, TenantDiscrimination, VirtualPersistentAttribute<O,J>

    public interface VirtualNavigable<J>
extends Navigable<J>
    Marker interface indicating that a particular Navigable represents a value not modeled as part of the application's domain model. This is generally values like discriminator, ROW_ID, Hibernate "back-refs", etc.
